==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Population
<hw>Pop`u*la"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>populatio</ets>: cf. F. <ets>population</ets>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>The act or process of populating; multiplication of
inhabitants.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>The whole number of people, or inhabitants, in a
country, or portion of a country; <as>as, a <ex>population</ex> of ten
millions</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Populator</ent>⟦br⟧
